data.description: Welcome in to this freshly updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Bryan where you'll immediately notice brand new vinyl flooring, fresh paint throughout, and amazing curb appeal with new landscaping and the cutest front door. This split floor plan places the primary suite with spacious bathroom and closet attached on one side and two guest bedrooms and full bath on the other. You will also love the outdoor spaces, being a cul-de-sac home with an oversized backyard. With its new floors, new microwave, new light fixtures, new blinds, new gas stove/oven and new dishwasher, four-year-old roof, and bright, fresh coat of paint, this house is ready to be called home sweet home!
